casebody.data:
Jefferson B. SESSIONS, III, Attorney General, et al., petitioners,
v.
Daniel BINDERUP, et al. No. 16-847. Supreme Court of the United States June 26, 2017.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.

Justice GINSBURG and Justice SOTOMAYOR would grant the petition for certiorari.
